Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,Note,,0,0,0,,毛澤東與赫魯曉夫 中蘇分裂的直接表現和深層原因 \NLecturer: 沈志华\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.00,Note,,0,0,0,,香港科技大學文化硏究中心, 2005
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.00,Note,,0,0,0,,This caption is generated by OpenAI Whisper model\N and reviewed by️ human
